source:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_SEQ_00<tab>Rampaging analas threaten the lives of shellfish gatherers at Hells' Lid.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラス・ジョブでのみ進行します。

碧のタマミズのズキンは、貝拾いの邪魔をされて困っているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_TODO_00<tab>Slay the kaen analas and goen anala.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_TODO_00<tab>獄之蓋の<var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA84901 /var>で見渡して<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADE01 /var>を討伐し
おびき寄せた<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADF01 /var>を討伐

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_000<tab>Hells' Lid is as unwelcoming a place as you are ever likely to find. Were it not for its abundance of shellfish, we would avoid it entirely.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>、助けてくれぇ～！
獄之蓋に「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADF01 /var>」が出たんだぁ～！
あんな熱い火の精に襲われたら、俺たち干からびちまうよぉ～！

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>Most of the creatures there will only turn to attack if we draw too close. However, the analas go to great lengths to hunt us down. Their ferocity is known throughout the Ruby Sea.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>けれど、あの辺りでは、いい貝が採れるんだぁ～。
商売のために必要なもんで、どうしても諦めたくねぇんだよぉ～。

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_002<tab>It is to you we must turn. Venture into their territory, slay any that confront you. A show of force should send the rest slinking back to their dens.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_002<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、すまねぇが、いっちょ討伐をお願いするぜぇ～！
獄之蓋で見渡して、現れた「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADE01 /var>」を倒していけば、
いずれ親玉の「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADF01 /var>」が現れるはずさぁ～。

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_019<tab>You are looking rather singed around the edges! Did the analas prove troublesome?
target: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_019<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADF01 /var>は倒してくれたかぁ～？

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>Glad tidings indeed. By your account, we have the shores of Hells' Lid to ourselves again. The area is safe for harvesting shellfish, for the time being at least.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>おぉ～、ばっちり倒してくれたんだなぁ～！
これで安心して、貝拾いが再開できるぞぉ～。

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Not only are they good for eating, but they are also used in the production of mother of pearl-inlaid pots. The Namazu gladly pay large sums for them, only to jump inside and stay there for hours on end.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>貝をたくさん集めたら、螺鈿細工の壺を作るんだぁ～。
ナマズオは壺の中に入るのが好きらしいからなぁ～、
綺麗な壺を作れば、きっと気に入ってくれるはずよぉ～。

source: TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_022<tab>Why? Perhaps the kami know, but I do not. I do know, however, that the analas will not be content to remain in their lairs like the Namazu in their pots. Should they emerge once more, we may require your aid.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN405_02989_ZUKIN_000_022<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、助けてくれてありがとなぁ～。
また<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F21ADF01 /var>が出たら、
<var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さんを頼らせてもらうぞぉ～！
